data.description: Welcome home!! As you walk into your new foyer you'll notice soaring ceilings, abundant natural light, and wide open spaces.  This home is wonderfully thought out, designed, and built. You'll notice lots of custom built is and no wasted space.  No detail was left out and quality is unmatched.  Your living room is the heart of the home; kitchen and dining room are an extension of that. Extended cabinetry, a walk in pantry, gas range and gorgeous granite are a few highlights in here.  Your owners suite, is just that, a suite... You have split vanities, an oversized tub, spacious shower and a closet that will hold EVERYTHING! Your closet connects to the laundry room where you'll find even more storage, racks, and a utility sink.  There is a drop zone and mudbench right inside the garage entry and again you're going to find even more storage. There is an office that is spacious enough to use a a play space or maybe even a guest room (currently used as a bedroom) and the hardwood floors carry in there too. Secondary bedrooms are in their own hall and have a massive linen closet and a shared bathroom with double vanities. The bedrooms are spacious and have wonderful closet space too (one is even a real walk in). You'll love this neighborhood and it's location, less than 3 minutes from the turnpike and less than 5 minutes from I-40 yet, you have no highway noise!   Come see this home today and let us help make it yours!!
